{"tid":157770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[jj插沙]成功戒癮嘅巴打請入","createTime":"2017-03-15T18:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T16:32:43.000Z","uid":90045,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a457e74cea1d24fabf9c9a6d924a9288da5bb8e","tid":157770,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"本人23歲  只要試做一樣嘢  就好容易上癮<br />\n做paper、打j、睇youtube片、食嘢、睇書、寫字、問候人......<br />\n<br />\n一款飯   因爲好味   連續食足半個月  仲覺得好正   然後搵到另一款麵 又食左半個月  <br />\n<br />\n寫篇文由22:00-21:00  唔識攰同餓<br />\n<br />\n總之一開始做 <br />\n就做好耐/好多次  要做到厭/辛苦/完成先會停    <br />\n<br />\n靜落黎諗  我好似冇左自己咁  不受控制<br />\n每次都要由一個癮轉另一個癮<br />\n而且連無聊嘢都會認真做<br />\n好易忘記正事    時間管理差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想知大家曾經有咩癮  點樣戒癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddd184ca0d0f66589b4ad2050ddd4f0f027c6a6","tid":157770,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b99c49c631f0d7094d8e87bd9b26e1a9156750","tid":157770,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4454846b15df275691fd8b6392c1ba2dd843ac","tid":157770,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"早知改做成唔成功都入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeca9bae27e96ec1a08f09c0445b8c93dc09ee49","tid":157770,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:16:53.000Z","msg":"屌我都係<br />\n好似呢個星期 我睇有線怪談<br />\n十年前既片<br />\n我用3日3夜 一口氣睇咩<img src=\"/ass