97e7fec10e","tid":157770,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打咁既精神應該係某方面成就會幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知專長係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都好想知 好想做就要做  分唔到輕重緩急<br />\n細個唔明點解要分文理科 樣樣都鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 會想一秒內知道全部內容<br />\n頭腦太多野唔識整合<br />\n如果有ironman果種 用投射 用手 可以用口控制 我人生應該會好成功<br />\n因為永遠口 同腦 快過手<br />\n語言能力寫 背  差過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得把口可以秒人"},{"pid":"185c623d82987f365bafe4e27625d6a0769a6922","tid":157770,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:29:05.000Z","msg":"補多樣 <br />\n細個寫日記  寫左兩星期頂唔順<br />\n因為每日嘅細節都有意義  好多啟發   <br />\n每篇都可以換下唔同寫作手法<br />\n結果每次都寫滿6mm嘅單行a4紙<br />\n寫個日記都3-4個鐘  冇晒精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44248033ed1eeb3d964922a01e51a223bf357fc5","tid":157770,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近排食煙肉食上癮...</blockquote><br />\n癲起上黎夜晚呢d時候專登落超級市場買包上黎食 唔食訓唔著<br />\n用焗爐焗1/3包 點知唔夠喉，又成間屋都係陣香味，聞聞下又忍唔住再整多d黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煙肉真係好唔健康 可以點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下豬場點樣屠宰啲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該會驚左<br />\n我唔敢食宵夜啊 最多食下紫菜 飲杯奶"},{"pid":"cbf11a8e3b4891781c903118118c65ce5202516f","tid":157770,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"諗緊如果有一樣野有價值 我又勁中意<br />\n一定可以做到好勁成績出黎 個腦會開足110%黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67fc96b43d6d4c25fa4b21d202a28224b51741d","tid":157770,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20